channel.title: Starting Fresh!
channel.description:
Okay, Hello. :)
Around 12 months ago I was right into the whole rsps scene, unfortunately I had to stop and started taking longer shifts at work etc. Well,, I want to get back in to it now that lifes settled down a bit.
From May 2012 to August 2012 I coded and maintained my own 317. I got over the 317 limitations and moved onto my own 474 server. From August to February 2013 I did the same. Due to real life issues I could no longer keep it up.
So, I'm curious if anyone would want to start up a new server with me, Help me get back into it. (A little motivation never hurt right? :) ) I have a fairly basic understanding of how it's all done. I do pick up and learn quite fast, I'm not expecting to get spoon fed everything.
I'd love to get back into it, I can do all the Graphics, Designs, Forums etc. easily.
From Australia, 18, Have skype. Not some retard but keen as fuck to do this. Hit me up if your keen!
